  "title": "Customer Operations Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Main Duties & Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Maintain strong working relationships with existing customers and act as the main point of coordination.</p></li><li><p>Manage daily customer operations, including order coordination and service delivery.</p></li><li><p>Handle customer enquiries related to orders, quotations, delivery schedules, shipping, and inventory availability.</p></li><li><p>Monitor issues and follow up to ensure timely resolution and continuity of service.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate closely with internal teams to meet customers’ operational requirements and manage expectations.</p></li><li><p>Prepare and provide weekly and monthly operational and business reports to management and customers.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Business or a related field.</p></li><li><p>At least 3 years of experience in order management or customer service.</p></li><li><p>Strong coordination, communication, and time management skills.</p></li><li><p>Detail-oriented, able to multitask, and a strong team player.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Application Details</strong></p><p>Kindly email your detailed resume in <strong>Word format</strong> to:<br /><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">candy.lim@peopleprofilers.com</a></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><strong>People Profilers Pte Ltd</strong><br />EA License No.: 02C4944<br />Registration No.: R1109829<br />DID: 6950 9738<br />20 Cecil Street, #08-09 PLUS Building, Singapore 049705<br /><a href=\"http://www.peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://www.peopleprofilers.com</a></p>",
